Isolated Sandbox Environments:
# Instantiate Local Platform Environment
python -m venv venv

# Activate Environment (Windows PowerShell Bypass)
venv\Scripts\activate

# Activate Environment (Mac/Linux Shells)
source venv/bin/activate


The Pip Package Manager Commands
Install Resource: pip install <package_name>
Freeze Dependencies: pip freeze > requirements.txt
Deploy From Configurations: pip install -r requirements.txt